#. welcome.storyWorkshop.goal
msgctxt "welcome.storyWorkshop.goal"
msgid "Develop connected speech — from single words to complete narratives."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.storyWorkshop.how
msgctxt "welcome.storyWorkshop.how"
msgid "Choose pictures, arrange them into a story, listen to the model and practice telling it yourself."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.storyWorkshop.purpose
msgctxt "welcome.storyWorkshop.purpose"
msgid "Narrative speech practice for DTTC's 'connected speech' phase. Build stories with pictures."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.syllableJump.goal
msgctxt "welcome.syllableJump.goal"
msgid "Develop syllable awareness and rhythmic speech planning."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.syllableJump.how
msgctxt "welcome.syllableJump.how"
msgid "See the word, tap each syllable in order. Clap along! Hear the whole word when all syllables are done."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.syllableJump.purpose
msgctxt "welcome.syllableJump.purpose"
msgid "Break words into syllables with visual and rhythmic cues. Support for children with neurodevelopmental conditions and childhood apraxia of speech."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.symbolText.goal
msgctxt "welcome.symbolText.goal"
msgid "To support reading comprehension and communication by linking text to visual symbols."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.symbolText.how
msgctxt "welcome.symbolText.how"
msgid "1. Type a sentence in the text box. 2. Tap \"Show with symbols\". 3. Each word is shown with a symbol above it. 4. Tap 🔊 for speech."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.symbolText.purpose
msgctxt "welcome.symbolText.purpose"
msgid "Symbol Text automatically shows pictograms above each word you type — inspired by Widgit. Perfect as reading support for children with autism or intellectual disabilities."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.talkBoard.goal
msgctxt "welcome.talkBoard.goal"
msgid "Give the child a voice and ability to communicate independently through picture and symbol support."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.talkBoard.how
msgctxt "welcome.talkBoard.how"
msgid "Tap pictures to speak. Build sentences in the strip at the top. Buttons have fixed positions (LAMP) and Fitzgerald Key colors: yellow=people, green=verbs, orange=things, blue=descriptions."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.talkBoard.purpose
msgctxt "welcome.talkBoard.purpose"
msgid "A communication board (AAC) for children with neurodevelopmental conditions who need support to express themselves. Based on core vocabulary with LAMP principles."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.talkingMat.goal
msgctxt "welcome.talkingMat.goal"
msgid "Give children the ability to express opinions and preferences, even with limited speech."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.talkingMat.how
msgctxt "welcome.talkingMat.how"
msgid "Drag pictures to zones: green (like), yellow (neutral) or red (dislike)."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.talkingMat.purpose
msgctxt "welcome.talkingMat.purpose"
msgid "Digital talking mat — a proven tool for expressing opinions by sorting pictures into zones."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.theMimic.goal
msgctxt "welcome.theMimic.goal"
msgid "Build motor speech planning through systematic imitation."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.theMimic.how
msgctxt "welcome.theMimic.how"
msgid "Listen to the model, mimic it. Start with simple sounds and work up to full sentences."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.theMimic.purpose
msgctxt "welcome.theMimic.purpose"
msgid "Core DTTC technique — listen and repeat with increasing complexity."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.timeTracker.goal
msgctxt "welcome.timeTracker.goal"
msgid "Increase time awareness and help with planning and transitions."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.timeTracker.how
msgctxt "welcome.timeTracker.how"
msgid "Start the timer at the beginning of an activity, see time displayed visually."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.timeTracker.purpose
msgctxt "welcome.timeTracker.purpose"
msgid "Track how long activities take with a visual timer."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.visualSupport.goal
msgctxt "welcome.visualSupport.goal"
msgid "Provide visual support that increases predictability and reduces the need for verbal instructions."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.visualSupport.how
msgctxt "welcome.visualSupport.how"
msgid "Choose a ready-made routine or create your own. Follow steps with pictures and text."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.visualSupport.purpose
msgctxt "welcome.visualSupport.purpose"
msgid "Visual schedules with step-by-step routines for common activities."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.visualTimer.goal
msgctxt "welcome.visualTimer.goal"
msgid "Make abstract time concepts concrete and visual, reduce anxiety around transitions."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.visualTimer.how
msgctxt "welcome.visualTimer.how"
msgid "Set a time, watch it decrease visually. First-then shows what happens next."
msgstr ""

#. welcome.visualTimer.purpose
msgctxt "welcome.visualTimer.purpose"
msgid "Visual countdown timer with first-then support."
msgstr ""

